data.description: Country home on 2 acres! Located on a paved road just 5 minutes from downtown Live Oak, you'll find this 3 bedroom 2 bath home on 2.03 acres. Enter the front door to see a gorgeous fireplace in the living room, spacious rooms, granite countertops with tile backsplash and a Florida room off the back overlooking the fenced back yard. The covered patio is perfect for grilling and enjoying the outdoors. The yard is fenced and cross fenced creating the perfect spot for animals. Farm shelter is already is place with water for your farm friends. The 50x40 metal building with half bath is the perfect spot for all your hobbies and toys. Inside the barn are additional rooms for an office AND storage space. This property offers a rural feel with the convenience of being minutes to town.
